    "publication": [
        {
            "abstract": "Â© 2017 Nature America, Inc. All rights reserved.The normalization of RNA-seq data is essential for accurate downstream inference, but the assumptions upon which most normalization methods are based are not applicable in the single-cell setting. Consequently, applying existing normalization methods to single-cell RNA-seq data introduces artifacts that bias downstream analyses. To address this, we introduce SCnorm for accurate and efficient normalization of single-cell RNA-seq data.",
